{"tid":1042268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：獲稅務補貼港澳居民只限高端及廣東所需人才","createTime":"2019-03-01T12:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T12:51:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c41e22330331d3043bc71ded7c75a5e2efd46f6","tid":1042268,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:28:40.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，到廣東省工作的港澳居民獲廣東省提供稅務補貼的措施，只限於高端人才，或廣東省需要的人才，而非所有到廣東省工作的港人。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，國務院副總理韓正要求，便利措施要符合社會要求，並作調研，以及獲相關部委同意。<br />\n<br />\n有關粵港澳大灣區的便利措施，主要圍繞便利港澳，希望盡量鼓勵港澳居民。她說，目前研究中的便利措施，亦不會有太多措施集中便利廣東省，同時部分便利措施亦不適用於廣東省，例如若廣東省車輛更便利到港澳，會造成兩地交通流量增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445572-20190301.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445572-20190301.htm&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CzBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=67cc8eb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445572-20190301.htm&h=3ef0ec0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445572-20190301.htm</a>"},{"pid":"37594d2c0c0e7342d70eb69a185e4288968d14a7","tid":1042268,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"打荷包唔得，打假身分證得？"},{"pid":"270a664c1f546527add5a2084d49d6edfb6a69d5","tid":1042268,"uid":64694,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:30:09.000Z","msg":"只限於高端人才<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n低端人唔當係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8e86c4954ce57f38aeece03e30392b3e0e7e65","tid":1042268,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37594d2c0c0e7342d70eb69a185e4288968d14a7","tid":1042268,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"打荷包唔得，打假身分證得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"印"},{"pid":"e1c